// Man page for print
manPrint="PRINT(1)                         X Shell Manual                         PRINT(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    print - Print text to terminal
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>print</b> TEXT
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Print text to screen. Internal func mainly used with command separator for
    command chaining and script output.
<b>OPTIONS</b>
    <b>TEXT</b> - Output
      Print text string to terminal.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>print Hello World</b>
    Display message

    <b>ls ; print Done listing files</b>
    Print after command
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>echo</b>"